Name: Rafael Romo
Nationality: Venezuela
Date of Birth: February 25, 1990
Position: Goalkeeper
Current club: DC United
MLS clubs played for: DC United
Rafael Romo is a goalkeeper at DC United who has played in 14 MLS matches in 2022 since joining the club on 27th April 2022, starting in 13 of these and coming on as a substitute on one occasion.

Romo last made an appearance in a competition game on August 20, playing 90 minutes for DC United against Philadelphia Union in a 6-0 loss. He has kept one MLS clean sheet this term. He has been shown one yellow card.
Romo played 17 First Division A games last season for OH Leuven, keeping two clean sheets.
Prior to moving to DC United in April 2022, Romo made 46 league appearances in total at OH Leuven.
